
## 🚀 DevOps Portfolio Project: Lumine Jewelry Store

📌 Project Title

Lumine Jewelry Store – CI/CD Automated Cloud Deployment on AWS


---

🧠 Project Overview (Portfolio Description)

A fully automated DevOps pipeline was built for a static e-commerce website (Lumine Jewelry Store) using GitHub Actions and AWS services. The project implements continuous integration and continuous deployment (CI/CD) to ensure every code change is automatically deployed to production with zero manual intervention.

The application is hosted on AWS S3 and delivered globally using CloudFront CDN with cache invalidation for instant updates.


---

🏗️ Architecture

Developer → GitHub → GitHub Actions → AWS S3 → CloudFront → End Users


---

⚙️ Tech Stack

Version Control: Git & GitHub

CI/CD: GitHub Actions

Cloud Provider: AWS

Storage: Amazon S3

CDN: Amazon CloudFront

Infrastructure: IAM, S3 policies, CloudFront invalidation

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Static Website)



---

🚀 Key Features

✔️ Fully automated CI/CD pipeline
✔️ Zero manual deployment
✔️ CloudFront CDN for fast global delivery
✔️ Automatic cache invalidation on updates
✔️ Secure S3 integration via IAM roles
✔️ Production-ready DevOps workflow


---

🔄 CI/CD Workflow

1. Developer pushes code to GitHub
2. GitHub Actions triggers pipeline
3. Code is synced to S3 bucket
4. CloudFront cache is invalidated
5. Updated website is live instantly


---

